ch prevents the earlier access from updating when this value changes over time.\n\nE:\\Projects\\ui test\\jarvis-unified - Copy\\apps\\desktop\\renderer\\src\\pages\\phone.tsx:57:11\n  55 |           setIp(lastDevice.ip)\n  56 |           setPort(lastDevice.port)\n> 57 |           connectToDevice(lastDevice.ip, lastDevice.port)\n     |           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ `connectToDevice` accessed before it is declared\n  58 |         }\n  59 |       }\n  60 |     })\n\nE:\\Projects\\ui test\\jarvis-unified - Copy\\apps\\desktop\\renderer\\src\\pages\\phone.tsx:88:3\n   86 |   }\n   87 |\n>  88 |   const connectToDevice = async (targetIp: string, targetPort: string) => {\n      |   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n>  89 |     if (!targetIp || !targetPort) return setErrorMsg('IP and Port are required.')\n      | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n>  90 |     setStatus('connecting')\n      …\n      | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n> 110 |     }\n      | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n> 111 |   }\n      | ^^^^ `connectToDevice` is declared here\n  112 |\n  113 |   const handleManualConnect = () => {\n  114 |     localStorage.setItem('jarvis_adb_ip', ip)",{"range":"37371","text":"26175"},{"range":"37372","text":"26210"},{"range":"37373","text":"26210"},{"range":"37374","text":"26175"},"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'connectToDevice'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["37375"],{"range":"37376","text":"26175"},{"range":"37377","text":"26210"},{"range":"37378","text":"26210"},{"range":"37379","text":"26210"},"Replace `'adb-get-notifications')␍` with `⏎········\"adb-get-notifications\",⏎······);`",{"range":"37380","text":"37381"},{"range":"37382","text":"26210"},{"range":"37383","text":"26175"},{"range":"37384","text":"26210"},{"range":"37385","text":"26210"}